{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":906,"text":"Hetain Patel: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11303,"text":"Yuyu Rau: Hi, I'm Hetain. I'm an artist."},{"time":14606,"text":"And this is Yuyu,"},{"time":16467,"text":"who is a dancer I have been working with."},{"time":18886,"text":"I have asked her to translate for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22492,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":27182,"text":"YR: If I may, I would like to tell you"},{"time":29890,"text":"a little bit about myself"},{"time":31620,"text":"and my artwork."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33916,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":39459,"text":"YR: I was born and raised near Manchester,"},{"time":42583,"text":"in England,"},{"time":43550,"text":"but I'm not going to say it in English to you,"},{"time":47122,"text":"because I'm trying to avoid any assumptions"},{"time":49883,"text":"that might be made from my northern accent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52965,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55540,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64975,"text":"YR: The only problem with masking it"},{"time":67487,"text":"with Chinese Mandarin"},{"time":69037,"text":"is I can only speak this paragraph,"},{"time":71755,"text":"which I have learned by heart"},{"time":73534,"text":"when I was visiting in China. (Laughter)"},{"time":76204,"text":"So all I can do is keep repeating it in different tones"},{"time":80092,"text":"and hope you won't notice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81952,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87301,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91481,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92848,"text":"YR: Needless to say, I would like to apologize"},{"time":95961,"text":"to any Mandarin speakers in the audience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102214,"text":"As a child, I would hate being made"},{"time":104887,"text":"to wear the Indian kurta pajama,"},{"time":107515,"text":"because I didn't think it was very cool."},{"time":110513,"text":"It felt a bit girly to me, like a dress,"},{"time":113814,"text":"and it had this baggy trouser part"},{"time":116472,"text":"you had to tie really tight"},{"time":118715,"text":"to avoid the embarrassment of them falling down."},{"time":122139,"text":"My dad never wore it,"},{"time":124175,"text":"so I didn't see why I had to."},{"time":127100,"text":"Also, it makes me feel a bit uncomfortable,"},{"time":130453,"text":"that people assume I represent something"},{"time":133148,"text":"genuinely Indian when I wear it,"},{"time":135474,"text":"because that's not how I feel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138923,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":144775,"text":"YR: Actually, the only way I feel comfortable"},{"time":147702,"text":"wearing it is by pretending"},{"time":150110,"text":"they are the robes of a kung fu warrior"},{"time":153321,"text":"like Li Mu Bai from that film,"},{"time":156060,"text":"\"Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":160373,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203383,"text":"Okay."},{"time":204992,"text":"So my artwork is about identity and language,"},{"time":212063,"text":"challenging common assumptions"},{"time":214793,"text":"based on how we look like or where we come from,"},{"time":219338,"text":"gender, race, class."},{"time":223082,"text":"What makes us who we are anyway?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226933,"text":"HP: (In Chinese)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":232880,"text":"YR: I used to read Spider-Man comics,"},{"time":235256,"text":"watch kung fu movies,"},{"time":236831,"text":"take philosophy lessons from Bruce Lee."},{"time":239616,"text":"He would say things like --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241265,"text":"HP: Empty your mind."},{"time":243352,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":244416,"text":"Be formless, shapeless, like water."},{"time":250429,"text":"Now you put water into a cup."},{"time":252419,"text":"It becomes the cup."},{"time":255315,"text":"You put water into a bottle, it becomes the bottle."},{"time":258422,"text":"Put it in a teapot, it becomes the teapot."},{"time":261801,"text":"Now, water can flow"},{"time":264450,"text":"or it can crash."},{"time":267100,"text":"Be water, my friend. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270455,"text":"YR: This year, I am 32 years old,"},{"time":274557,"text":"the same age Bruce Lee was when he died."},{"time":277676,"text":"I have been wondering recently,"},{"time":280270,"text":"if he were alive today,"},{"time":282200,"text":"what advice he would give me"},{"time":284226,"text":"about making this TED Talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288170,"text":"HP: Don't imitate my voice."},{"time":291908,"text":"It offends me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293979,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":296009,"text":"YR: Good advice,"},{"time":297760,"text":"but I still think that we learn who we are"},{"time":301472,"text":"by copying others."},{"time":303575,"text":"Who here hasn't imitated their childhood hero"},{"time":307792,"text":"in the playground, or mum or father?"},{"time":311687,"text":"I have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313948,"text":"HP: A few years ago, in order to make this video"},{"time":318490,"text":"for my artwork, I shaved off all my hair"},{"time":322495,"text":"so that I could grow it back as my father had it"},{"time":325638,"text":"when he first emigrated from India"},{"time":328404,"text":"to the U.K. in the 1960s."},{"time":331668,"text":"He had a side parting and a neat mustache."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335798,"text":"At first, it was going very well."},{"time":338417,"text":"I even started to get discounts in Indian shops."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341467,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345468,"text":"But then very quickly,"},{"time":347092,"text":"I started to underestimate"},{"time":348839,"text":"my mustache growing ability,"},{"time":350519,"text":"and it got way too big."},{"time":353921,"text":"It didn't look Indian anymore."},{"time":356668,"text":"Instead, people from across the road,"},{"time":358511,"text":"they would shout things like --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360402,"text":"HP and YR: Arriba! Arriba! Ándale! Ándale!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362618,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":364619,"text":"HP: Actually, I don't know why I am even talking like this."},{"time":366983,"text":"My dad doesn't even have an Indian accent anymore."},{"time":369987,"text":"He talks like this now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372514,"text":"So it's not just my father that I've imitated."},{"time":376542,"text":"A few years ago I went to China for a few months,"},{"time":380140,"text":"and I couldn't speak Chinese,"},{"time":382974,"text":"and this frustrated me,"},{"time":384786,"text":"so I wrote about this and had it translated"},{"time":388738,"text":"into Chinese, and then I learned this by heart,"},{"time":395225,"text":"like music, I guess."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398422,"text":"YR: This phrase is now etched into my mind"},{"time":401763,"text":"clearer than the pin number to my bank card,"},{"time":404642,"text":"so I can pretend I speak Chinese fluently."},{"time":408570,"text":"When I had learned this phrase,"},{"time":410618,"text":"I had an artist over there hear me out"},{"time":413354,"text":"to see how accurate it sounded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415823,"text":"I spoke the phrase, and then he laughed"},{"time":418309,"text":"and told me, \"Oh yeah, that's great,"},{"time":421120,"text":"only it kind of sounds like a woman.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":423493,"text":"I said, \"What?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":424955,"text":"He said, \"Yeah, you learned from a woman?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":428877,"text":"I said, \"Yes. So?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":430881,"text":"He then explained the tonal differences"},{"time":433522,"text":"between male and female voices"},{"time":435772,"text":"are very different and distinct, and that I had learned it very well,"},{"time":439574,"text":"but in a woman's voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441567,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443790,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":451100,"text":"HP: Okay. So this imitation business"},{"time":454519,"text":"does come with risk."},{"time":456204,"text":"It doesn't always go as you plan it,"},{"time":458912,"text":"even with a talented translator."},{"time":462382,"text":"But I am going to stick with it,"},{"time":464668,"text":"because contrary to what we might usually assume,"},{"time":469033,"text":"imitating somebody can reveal something unique."},{"time":473132,"text":"So every time I fail"},{"time":476387,"text":"to become more like my father,"},{"time":478943,"text":"I become more like myself."},{"time":482838,"text":"Every time I fail to become Bruce Lee,"},{"time":487420,"text":"I become more authentically me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491066,"text":"This is my art."},{"time":492551,"text":"I strive for authenticity,"},{"time":495871,"text":"even if it comes in a shape"},{"time":498106,"text":"that we might not usually expect."},{"time":501802,"text":"It's only recently that I've started to understand"},{"time":506038,"text":"that I didn't learn to sit like this"},{"time":509745,"text":"through being Indian."},{"time":511891,"text":"I learned this from Spider-Man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515167,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516905,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518462,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}